## Objective
The objective of this lab is to correctly activate the appropriate subscription. The next step is to create a functional management group. A role assignment is required for members within the management group. These members can have built in and custom roles applied to them. I can review the activity logs of any changes that are made to these roles and role assignents.

## What I did
1. I reviewed my subscription access level and enabled access management for Azure resources.
2. I created a management group.
3. I created a role assignment for a member in the management group.
4. I Created a custom role and can apply this to the member.
5. I can review the activity logs of the creation and changes made to these roles.

